            <para>
              <text>All that piece of land containing 512.6981 hectares, more or less, situated in Blocks IX and X, Maramarua Survey District, being Sections 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5, SO Plan 58118, and being all the land comprised and described in certificate of title No. 56D/715 (South Auckland Registry).</text>
