        <para>
          <label-para skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="no">16</label>
            <para>
              <text>All that piece of land containing 95.2529 hectares, more or less, situated in Blocks IX, X, and XIII, Cambridge Survey District, being Lot 2 on Deposited Plan 29655, and being all the land comprised and described in certificate of title No. 47A/808 (South Auckland Registry).</text>
