        <para>
          <label-para skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="no">17</label>
            <para>
              <text>All that piece of land containing 2 roods 2.63 perches, more or less, being Lots 1 and 2, Deposited Plan 21509, and Lots 3 and 4, Deposited Plan 19075, and being part Sections 43 and 44, Township of Hamilton West, excepting pursuant to section 19, Public Works Act 1928, any mines of coal and other minerals not taken by Proclamation S. 165717, and being all the land comprised and described in certificate of title No. 1B/528 (South Auckland Registry).</text>
